Package: CVtools
Title: Tools related to preparation and analysis of academic CVs.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Francisco Rodriguez-Sanchez <f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package contains tools and functions to help prepare a modern, dynamic academic CV
    (with citations, altmetrics, etc), plus CV analysis tools (e.g. citation or coauthorship networks).
    It is particularly aimed for CVs maintained in Rmarkdown format.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: CC-BY-NC-SA
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/Pakillo/CVtools
BugReports: https://github.com/Pakillo/CVtools/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:
    knitr (>= 1.5),
    rmarkdown
Suggests:
    knitcitations (>= 0.6),
    testthat
